window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Now a major motion picture starring Michael B. Jordan - watch now on Prime Video!</p> <p>From Tom Clancy, the celebrated author of the Jack Ryan series, comes the number one <i>New York Times</i> best seller that puts CIA operative John Clark front and center...</p> <p>His code name is Mr. Clark. His work for the CIA is brilliant, cold-blooded. and efficient...But who is he really?</p> <p>In a harrowing tour de force, Tom Clancy shows how an ordinary man named John Kelly crossed the lines of justice and morality to become the CIA legend, Mr. Clark.</p> <p>It is an unforgettable journey into the heart of darkness. Without mercy. Without guilt. Without remorse.</p>"; 
